::Spears::

Walks over to Striker.  Still trying to fight the program, but is 
failing.  She puts her hand on Strikers shoulder and looks at him.  
She didn't want to do this, but she had no choice in the matter.  She 
leaned down and picked up Striker, carring him over her shoulder.  
She felt her spark breaking as she did this.  She stopped for a 
second and looked at Tamron.  She didn't want to turn Striker over to 
Tamron,  but the chip overroad her own programs.  She just stood 
there, holding Striker, looking at Tamron.
